{"tid":1472862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推818民陣遊行] 每位1/2000000，我地需要你！","createTime":"2019-08-14T16:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:12:06.000Z","uid":273980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee5bb2af6b8ac5d9e1c3f683db381e39e9bd9e1","tid":1472862,"uid":273980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"呢幾個星期，及至呢兩個月，大家都憤怒過、傷心過、沮喪過、無力過。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日好多人講「黃藍係立場，但黑白係良知」，正正係無數警暴畫面再次觸動到好多搖擺派、淺黃淺藍、和理非，重燃佢地上街的諗法，而818正正需要佢地。<br />\n<br />\n818要有二百萬！或更多！要話俾政府聽不論係五大訴求的初衷定唔同崗位的手足，我地都無放棄過！我地係言而有信，不撤不散！亦話俾政府聽，我地都想和平，只要你回應，我地無人想暴力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/15/003924_23a3a1fa07296dd7eecc249a89e6d574.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2F003924_23a3a1fa07296dd7eecc249a89e6d574.png&h=4a4cd710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05489ca64656039938fcf78835f7ec82d893cf08","tid":1472862,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n到時見"},{"pid":"edd3376259eeb74bda024386b47d7ba29e63fba8","tid":1472862,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkRgLwS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkRgLwS.png&h=cee86880&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTN7R5o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTN7R5o.jpg&h=b076ef80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c376a7d519ca181de7227df970ddf727112e8a45","tid":1472862,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思各位，借個位宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">818百萬人大遊行<br />\n黑警還眼<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家開始全民投入宣傳工作<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">各區連儂牆、airdrop、派街招、擺街站<br />\nfacebook instagram瘋狂轉貼文宣</span></span></strong><br />\n文宣source: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=a27e10f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=6148caca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重要日程：</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n8月15日：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）<br />\n8月16日：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n8月17日：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n8月17日：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月18日：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></span></strong><br />\n8月24日：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）<br />\n8月25日：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）<br />\n各位手足，到時見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fceb34664e4443cee1a9c20746a7884d85866208","tid":1472862,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9187eeb30168b227392ac9e3e9f0116f645b4dbc","tid":1472862,"uid":95064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:11:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c06d6449f87163e530e8e8cf7060dbfa4e839023","tid":1472862,"uid":95064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"推"}]}